{"word":"G5422 - φρεναπατάω - phrenapatáō - fren-ap-at-ah'-o - Deceive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φρεναπατάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phrenapatáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fren-ap-at-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Deceive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வஞ்சி"},{"paragraph":"to deceive anyone's mind"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5423 - φρεναπάτης - phrenapátēs - fren-ap-at'-ace/5423\">G5423</a>; to <i>be a mind misleader</i>, that is, <i>delude:</i> - deceive.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}